Yes. I do. I'm a reporter.
Yes. 我是. 我是记者.

3
00:00:17,528 --> 00:00:18,186
Where's the camera?
摄像机在哪儿?

4
00:00:19,255 --> 00:00:20,886
Oh,I'm not a TV reporter.
Oh, 我不是电视记者. 

5
00:00:21,254 --> 00:00:22,814
-I'm a radio reporter. -Oh.
-我是个电台记者. -Oh.

6
00:00:23,952 --> 00:00:24,859
Are you disappointed?
你失望了吗?

7
00:00:25,731 --> 00:00:26,438
Did something happen?
出了什么事吗?

8
00:00:27,370 --> 00:00:29,243
Do you mean,like a fire?
你的意思是, 类似于火灾?

9
00:00:30,190 --> 00:00:31,698
No. I'm doing an interview.
No. 我要进行一个采访

10
00:00:32,217 --> 00:00:33,319
That's part of my job,too.
那是我工作的一部分, too.

11
00:00:34,080 --> 00:00:34,980
How come you're a reporter?
你是怎么成为一名记者的?

12
00:00:35,502 --> 00:00:36,771
Oh, I like this job.
Oh, 我喜欢这份工作.

13
00:00:37,218 --> 00:00:38,904
I used to work in an office.I hated that.
我以前的工作坐在办公室. 我讨厌那样.

14
00:00:39,429 --> 00:00:39,729
Yeah? 
Yeah? 

15
00:00:40,077 --> 00:00:41,489
Yeah. I worked in the mailroom.
Yeah. 那时我在收发室工作.

16
00:00:41,770 --> 00:00:43,515
I was in that one room all day,you know? 
我在一个房子里呆一整天, 你知道吗?

17
00:00:44,356 --> 00:00:45,105
So I quit that job.
所以我辞了那个工作.

18
00:00:45,736 --> 00:00:46,520
Guess what I did next.
猜猜我接下来做了什么. 

19
00:00:46,975 --> 00:00:47,433
What?
做什么?

20
00:00:47,753 --> 00:00:50,484
